quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  21,36,"Nígbà tí àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ bá rí ọ, wọn kò sì níí kà ọ́ kún kiní kan bí kò ṣe oníyẹ̀yẹ́ pé: “Ṣé èyí ni ẹni tó ń sọ̀rọ̀ nípa àwọn ọlọ́hun yín?” Aláìgbàgbọ́ sì ni àwọn náà nípa ìrántí Àjọkẹ́-ayé.",""
  21,37,"Wọ́n fi ìkánjú sínú àdámọ́ ènìyàn. Mo máa fi àwọn àmì Mi hàn yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ má ṣe kán Mi lójú.",""
  21,38,"Wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ìgbà wo ni àdéhùn yìí yóò ṣẹ tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo?”",""
  21,39,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ mọ ìgbà tí wọn kò níí dá Iná dúró níwájú wọn àti ní ẹ̀yìn wọn, tí A ò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́, (wọn ìbá tí wá ìyà pẹ̀lú ìkánjú).",""
  21,40,"Ṣùgbọ́n (ìyà Iná) yóò bá wọn ní òjijì, nígbà náà ó máa kó ìdààmú bá wọn; wọn kò sì níí lè dá a padà. A kò sì níí sún (ìyà náà) síwájú fún wọn.",""
  21,41,"Wọ́n kúkú ti fi àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ kan ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ ṣíwájú rẹ! Nítorí náà, ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ sì dìyà tó yí àwọn tó ń fi wọ́n ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ po.",""
  21,42,"Sọ pé: “Ta ni ẹni tí ó ń ṣọ yín ní òru àti ní ọ̀sán níbi ìyà Àjọkẹ́-ayé?” Àmọ́ ńṣe ni wọ́n ń gbúnrí kúrò níbi ìrántí Olúwa wọn.",""
  21,43,"Tàbí wọ́n ní àwọn ọlọ́hun kan tó máa gbà wọ́n sílẹ̀ lẹ́yìn Wa ni? Wọn kò lè ran ara wọn lọ́wọ́. Wọn kò sì lè gbà wọ́n sílẹ̀ lọ́dọ̀ Wa.",""
  21,44,"Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ A fún àwọn wọ̀nyí àti àwọn bàbá wọn ní ìgbádùn títí ìṣẹ̀mí ayé wọn fi gùn. Ṣé wọn kò rí i pé dájúdájú Àwa l’À ń mú ilẹ̀ dínkù (mọ́ àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ lọ́wọ́) láti àwọn etí ìlú (wọnú ìlú nípa fífún àwọn mùsùlùmí ní ìṣẹ́gun lórí wọn). Nítorí náà, ṣé àwọn ni wọ́n máa borí ni?",""
